data.description: Move in ready 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom home with a bonus room in beautiful North Augusta. 2.99% assumable VA loan!   Established neighborhood that still has trees and greenery.  Convenient to I-20 so perfect for military or medical.  Rocking chair front porch and back patio are perfect for relaxing.  Fenced backyard.  Do not miss this great home!
